long_description: custom decals yyc is calgary's leading one stop automotive restyling shop lead by a passionate team of creative designers and expert installers. from starting in our bedroom making decals for our friends and car crews back in 2010, we came together and wanted to offer calgary's car scene an experience they have never seen before. fast forward to 2018, custom decals yyc was incorporated and started its journey at the new horizon mall. from just making small stickers, we now offer a wide variety of services including; window tinting, paint protection film, vehicle wrapping, wide body installs and commercial graphics. turning your ideas into reality. we love giving back to the community because that is a big part of custom decals yyc and who we are. together, shawn and ryan started this company for the love & passion they had for cars. with over 5 years of full-time auto body experience, nicholas has taken apart and put together over thousands of vehicles. contact us today to get started.
